ca.ualberta.taskr

Class NearbyTasksActivity

  • ca.ualberta.taskr.NearbyTasksActivity

  • public class NearbyTasksActivity

    Displays a map with markers for all tasks within 5km of the current user's location. Popups displaying task information are shown when markers are clicked, and tapping these popups opens a class ViewTaskActivity for that task.

    See Also:
    class ViewTaskActivity

        public void onMapReady(com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.maps.MapboxMap mapboxMap)
